    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute dream of a ride. It is in truly incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous about keeping it pristine, so it's basically flawless inside and out. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I promise you\u2019re going to love every single mile in it. Feel free to reach out if you want to chat or come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
