    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition\u2014the leather is supple with no creasing, the carpets are pristine, and every electronic component operates with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting its pampered history. For the discerning buyer who settles for nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
