    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect of this asset, from its flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, has been meticulously maintained to meet the highest standards of excellence. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of uncompromising quality that performs with the same precision as the day it left the assembly line. We invite discerning buyers to inspect this investment-grade vehicle and experience its peerless mechanical integrity firsthand.",
      "price": 44500.0,
